      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «مَكْتُوبٌ عَلَى بَابِ اَلْجَنَّةِ اَلصَّدَقَةُ بِعَشَرَةٍ وَ اَلْقَرْضُ بِثَمَانِيَةَ عَشَرَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1697 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"It is written on the gate of Paradise: Charity is rewarded tenfold, and a loan is rewarded eighteenfold.\""
        ]
